---
// Pure-CSS phone mockup — no screenshot dependency.
// Mirrors the in-app feed shell: brand bar, search field, semantic cards.
---

<div class="phone" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="phone-body">
    <div class="status">
      <span>9:41</span>
      <span class="status-icons">
        <span class="dot" />
        <span class="dot" />
        <span class="bar" />
      </span>
    </div>

    <div class="appbar">
      <span class="brand-mark">Dualio</span>
      <span class="avatar" />
    </div>

    <div class="search">
      <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="7"></circle><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"></line></svg>
      <span>Find anything you saved…</span>
    </div>

    <article class="card">
      <span class="meta">ARTICLE · 4 MIN READ</span>
      <h4>The Quiet Revolution of Slow Architecture</h4>
      <p>In an era obsessed with speed and immediate gratification, a new movement is taking root.</p>
      <span class="footer-meta">Added 2 hours ago</span>
    </article>

    <article class="card recipe">
      <span class="badge">RECIPE</span>
      <div class="thumb"></div>
      <h4>No-Knead Olive Sourdough</h4>
      <span class="meta">18h prep · high difficulty</span>
    </article>

    <article class="card quote">
      <span class="meta">HIGHLIGHT</span>
      <blockquote>"Simplicity is the ultimate sophistication."</blockquote>
      <span class="meta cite">— Leonardo da Vinci</span>
    </article>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .phone {
    --phone-w: 280px;
    --phone-r: 36px;
    width: var(--phone-w);
    aspect-ratio: 9 / 19;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-radius: var(--phone-r);
    padding: 10px;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, #2a2a2c 0%, #111113 100%);
    box-shadow:
      0 36px 72px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18),
      0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08),
      inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    position: relative;
  }

  .phone::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 14px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 96px;
    height: 22px;
    background: #050506;
    border-radius: 999px;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .phone-body {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--surface);
    border-radius: calc(var(--phone-r) - 8px);
    padding: 36px 14px 14px;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
  }

  .status {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--on-surface);
    padding: 0 6px;
    margin-top: -4px;
  }

  .status-icons {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .status .dot {
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--on-surface);
  }

  .status .bar {
    width: 16px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    border: 1px solid var(--on-surface);
    position: relative;
  }

  .status .bar::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 1px;
    width: 70%;
    background: var(--on-surface);
    border-radius: 1px;
  }

  .appbar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 4px 6px;
  }

  .brand-mark {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .avatar {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--surface-container-high);
    border: 1px solid var(--outline-variant);
  }

  .search {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 9px 12px;
    background: var(--surface-container);
    border-radius: 999px;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--surface-container-lowest);
    border: 1px solid var(--outline-variant);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .meta {
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .card h4 {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.25;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--on-surface);
  }

  .card p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 11px;
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
  }

  .footer-meta {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .recipe {
    padding: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .recipe .badge {
    position: absolute;
    margin: 8px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.78);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .recipe .thumb {
    height: 78px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c9a36b 0%, #8b5a2b 60%, #4a2c14 100%);
  }

  .recipe h4 {
    padding: 8px 14px 0;
  }

  .recipe .meta {
    padding: 0 14px 12px;
  }

  .quote blockquote {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--on-surface);
  }

  .quote .cite {
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: normal;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 10px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 880px) {
    .phone {
      --phone-w: 240px;
    }
  }
</style>
